author: Dave Skretta, Ap Sports Writer
title: Keselowski wins pole for Sprint Cup race at Kansas
text: Photo: Colin E. Braley, AP NASCAR Sprint Cup Series auto racing driver Brad Keselowski heads down pit road during a practice session at Kansas Speedway in Kansas City, Kan., Friday, Oct. 16, 2015. NASCAR Sprint Cup Series auto racing driver Brad Keselowski heads... KANSAS CITY, Kan. (AP) — Brad Keselowski won the pole for Sunday's Sprint Cup race at Kansas Speedway, though he was quick to acknowledge it's where he finishes in the crucial Chase race that matters.
